	<ThingDef ParentName="BodyPartBionicBase">
		<defName>TSOA_BioferriteArm</defName>
		<label>bioferrite clawed arm</label>
		<description>An arm made of bioferrite, ending in clawed fingers. The psychically-reactive metal is animated by its psychic attunement to the user. Becomes sharper and more dangerous as the user's psychic powers grow, growing more effective as a weapon but less effective for work. Replacing human parts with bioferrite also has deleterious effects on the psyche, driving the user closer to madness.</description>
